query:
SELECT a.*, e.tipoEvento, e.dataEvento, f.nome as formandoNome 
FROM agendamento a 
INNER JOIN evento e ON a.eventoId = e.id 
INNER JOIN formando f ON a.formandoId = f.id 
WHERE e.turmaId = (SELECT id FROM turma WHERE codigo = '553') 
LIMIT 10
